- The strength difference is the gap between the strongest and weakest teams based on these metrics.

- "pinnacle of success" refers to the highest rank based on total points scored by players;
- "well-oiled machine" refers to a team that performs efficiently and effectively;
- "combined strength" refers to the total points scored by all players on the team.

